  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Faith, Race and Hate Crime Grants scheme announces £1.8 million in project support
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Faith Minister Lord Greenhalgh has announced the projects which will receive funding.</p>

  </div>
</div>

<div class="govuk-grid-row">
  <div class="metadata-logo-wrapper">
    <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds metadata-column">
        <div class="app-c-publisher-metadata" lang="en">
    <div class="app-c-published-dates " lang="en">
    Published 17 November 2020
    <br></br>Last updated 17 November 2020
      — <a href="#history" class="app-c-published-dates__history-link govuk-link">see all updates</a>
</div>

